[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。この顔ぶれでのお茶会は、やはり格別ですわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あら？　あなたには、ミーケとディオーナが\nいるじゃないの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "友との親愛と臣下との絆は、異なるもの。\nクリセルダなら、よく知っているでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。私たちは同志にして友。\nだからこそ、このお茶会は得難いものだわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ルアッカ",
		"romanized_name": "RUAKKA",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "女子会っていうんだよな？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。ルアッカとムラサキは遠慮してくださいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ムラサキ",
		"romanized_name": "MURASAKI",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "言われなくても遠慮するさ。\nこう見えて、作法は心得ているからね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "二人が、ごめんね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "いいのよ、アンチュ。さ、二人とも召し上がれ。\n新作を用意してみたのだけど、どれが好きかしら？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら、かわいらしいクッキーですわね。\nこれは……木の実を混ぜ込んでいますのね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。軽い食感の木の実を薄く切って、\n少し重めにした本体に混ぜ込んでみたの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "軽妙な食感ながら、物足りなさを感じさせない采配。\nふふ。また腕を上げましたわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "こっちは……もぐっ……\nふわふわでサクサク……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふむ。ララは複雑な食感で、味が濃厚なもの、\nアンチュは意外に軽い口当たりが好き……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ね、ねえ。クリセルダは何が一番好き？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "え、私？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "だ、だって……作ったクリセルダは\nどれが一番お気に入りなのか知りたくて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "うーん、そうね。このほろ苦さは、我ながら\n作っていて癖になったわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ほろ苦さ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "そうそう。こっちの食感も、なかなか上手くいったと\n思うのよ。パリッとしつつ、中はホロッとね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "パリッと……ホロホロ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "クリセルダは以前から、お茶会のたびに\nお菓子を手ずから振る舞ってくれましたわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。かわいくて美味しいものを作るのは楽しいもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "それをこうして、かわいい子たちが食べてくれる姿を\n間近で見られるのは本望ね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら。わたくしまでかわいいと？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "美しさとかわいらしさは同時に成り立つものね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "はぁ。相変わらずの人たらしですわね。\n錬金党に迎えられた当初は、驚きましたのよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "怜悧なあなたが、進んでかわいらしいお菓子や料理を\n振る舞う姿は、あまりに意外でしたもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あら。私の印象なんて、私自身は関知できないものよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。渇望一筋の人生でなければ、意外と今頃、\nいいお嫁さんになっていたかもしれませんね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ク、クリセルダは……お嫁さんになりたいの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "うっ！　そ、その上目遣いは反則よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "私はアンチュのような、かわいい子のお嫁さんになら\nなりたいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "えへへ……じゃあ、クリセルダのお婿さんになるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ララ・トロッケル",
		"romanized_name": "Lara Trockel",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "元「極夜の錬金党」の錬金術士。現在は\n「ララ・キングダム」の王として精力的に活動している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]